  <thing id="fPTMarkGlo" name="Marked for Glory (m)" description="From the moment your birth you were destined for glory beyond mere morals.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: 1st level character, Iron Will, Great Fortitude, or Lightning Reflexes.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You gain the ability to use mythic power once per day (see page 4), adding 1d6 to any die roll after it is made and the results are revealed. If you ever gain mythic tiers, you can use your mythic power one additional time per day." compset="Feat" summary="1/day you can add 1d6 to any die roll after its made." uniqueness="useronce">
