  <thing id="fPTWepFine" name="Weapon Finesse (m)" description="You are an expert with weapons that rely on your agility.\n\n{b}Prerequisite{/b}: Weapon Finesse, 1st mythic tier.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: You can use your Dexterity score on melee attack rolls and damage rolls when using a finesse weapon instead of your Strength score.\n\n{B}Note:{/B} Jason Bulmahn has confirmed that this feat was to only affect Finesse capable weapons." compset="Feat" summary="Use Dex to hit and damage with finesse weapons." uniqueness="useronce">
